headline: Date Set For Moody's Earnings Release And Investor Teleconference
summary: NEW YORK, July 09, 2025--Moody's Corporation (NYSE: MCO) will release its second quarter 2025 results before the start of NYSE trading on Wednesday, July 23, 2025. A copy of the earnings release and supplemental presentation slides will be posted on Moody's Investor Relations website, ir.moodys.com.
